      <section class="mt-16 rounded-xl border border-emerald-500/20 bg-emerald-500/5 p-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="text-[11px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-emerald-300">Next honest step</div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-slate-100">
          Turn the easiest agent passport into one bounded execution lane
