        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          GitHub unlocking more surfaces is useful, but the next real decision is whether one governed workflow can run end to end without broad connector sprawl, hidden credential drift, or loose authority.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <a
            href="/blog/capability-first-agent-onboarding?rhumb_experiment=e004&rhumb_source=agent-passport-onboarding"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-400 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-display font-semibold text-navy hover:bg-emerald-300 transition-colors duration-200"
