            GitHub or SSO getting an agent through the front door does not answer what breaks inside unattended loops, how shared provider budgets get contained once multiple agents reuse the same rail, or how credentials stay narrow after the first successful login. These three pages carry the passport ranking into live operator constraints.
          </p>
          <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
            <a href="/blog/llm-apis-agent-loops" class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-navy/60 p-4 transition-colors hover:border-slate-700">
